      "message": "Are you sure that you don\u0027t want to do one of the following?\n\nA.\n  \"notifiers\": {\n    \"email\": [\n      {\n        \"filter\": \"warning\",\n        \"emails\": [\"borenet@gmail.com\"]\n      },\n    ],\n    \"chat\": [\n      {\n        \"filter\": \"debug\",\n        \"room\": \"autoroll-test\"\n      }\n    ],\n  },\n\nB.\n  \"email_notifiers\": [\n    {\n      \"filter\": \"warning\",\n      \"emails\": [\"borenet@gmail.com\"]\n    },\n  ],\n  \"chat_notifiers\": [\n    {\n      \"filter\": \"debug\",\n      \"room\": \"autoroll-test\"\n    }\n  ],\n\nC.\n  \"notifiers\": [\n    {\n      \"email\": {\n        \"emails\": [\"borenet@gmail.com\"],\n      },\n      \"filter\": \"warning\",\n    },\n    {\n      \"chat\": {\n        \"room\": \"autoroll-test\"\n      },\n      \"filter\": \"debug\",\n    }\n  ],\n\nD.\nstruct Notifier {\n  type    string  // or enum\n  filter  notifier.Filter\n  subject string\n  // Fields only applicable when type\u003d\u003d\"email\"\n  emails []string\n  markup string\n  // Fields only applicable when type\u003d\u003d\"chat\"\n  room string\n}",
